00:01:47.639 --> 00:01:48.801
Poljubček. Se vidimo.

00:01:48.890 --> 00:01:50.597
Rad te imam.
–Adijo, očka.

00:01:51.850 --> 00:01:55.676
V redu? Se vidiva.
–Adijo.

00:02:36.687 --> 00:02:40.021
Kolega, nalagam.

00:02:54.872 --> 00:02:56.911
Jutro!
Velik oboževalec sem, g. Harris!

00:03:11.513 --> 00:03:13.173
<i>Ne verjamem v usodo.

00:03:13.264 --> 00:03:14.509
SNEMAM

00:03:14.599 --> 00:03:16.342
Ne v karmo, naključja,

00:03:16.435 --> 00:03:19.008
teorije zarote in to sranje.

00:03:19.562 --> 00:03:21.223
Sranje se pač zgodi.

00:03:21.314 --> 00:03:22.528
In življenje?

00:03:24.193 --> 00:03:25.390
Je samo sranje, ki se zgodi,

00:03:25.485 --> 00:03:28.820
ko si želiš, da bi bil nekdo drug
ali nekje drugje.

00:03:37.331 --> 00:03:38.706
S kom si govoril?

00:03:38.789 --> 00:03:41.115
Z nikomer,
po telefonu sem brkljal.

00:03:42.002 --> 00:03:43.829
Kaj počenjaš zunaj?

00:03:45.504 --> 00:03:46.998
Saj ne kadiš spet, kajne?

00:03:47.090 --> 00:03:49.841
Mama, saj veš, da ne.

00:03:49.925 --> 00:03:53.461
V moji sobi postane zadušljivo.
Pa grem na svež zrak.

00:04:03.939 --> 00:04:05.399
Nisi nečesa pozabil?

00:04:06.818 --> 00:04:07.848
Danes sem brez glave.

00:04:07.943 --> 00:04:10.269
Izvoli, celo očistila sem jih.

00:04:10.362 --> 00:04:12.438
Hvala, ljubica.
Ne vem, kaj bi brez tebe.

00:04:12.532 --> 00:04:13.776
Ne vem, zakaj jih še nosiš.

00:04:13.866 --> 00:04:15.740
Saj samo kričiš
in stokaš s strani.

00:04:15.826 --> 00:04:18.399
Kaj? Čudovite igre jih učim.

00:04:18.495 --> 00:04:20.240
Danes jih potrebujem za tekanje

00:04:20.331 --> 00:04:21.612
zaradi prošenj za sponzorstvo,

00:04:21.707 --> 00:04:24.792
da ti bodo očetje dali
kupe denarja za tvoj dogodek.

00:04:25.879 --> 00:04:27.502
Pusti to.

00:04:27.588 --> 00:04:29.665
Preveri, če Ravi ve kaj novega.

00:04:30.091 --> 00:04:31.716
Bom.

00:04:31.800 --> 00:04:33.627
Kar meni prepusti.

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:35.177
Adijo, ljubica.

00:04:48.860 --> 00:04:51.148
Jutro, gospodje! Kako smo?

00:04:51.237 --> 00:04:53.028
Ste dobro? Kako je, Hal?

00:04:53.113 --> 00:04:54.572
