Mami, nič ni. Spodrsnilo mi je.
Nekaj sem popil.

00:13:38.341 --> 00:13:40.250
S kom si bil?
–S Seanom.

00:13:40.344 --> 00:13:41.719
Pameten fant je.

00:13:42.763 --> 00:13:45.052
Gotovo se njemu to ni zgodilo.

00:13:45.139 --> 00:13:47.809
