Popoln kreten.

00:15:09.849 --> 00:15:11.259
Verjetno si zato tukaj.

00:15:11.350 --> 00:15:12.630
Pogrešaš me.

00:15:12.726 --> 00:15:14.767
Končno si podlegla …

